sub_title: Senior Patent Attorney | European and Dutch Patent Attorney | High Tech
summary:
European and Dutch patent attorney.
Patent preparation and prosecution, patentability, infringement, and validity in US and Europe in various fields of electronics, physics, and computer science, such as e.g. semiconductors (including IC manufacturing), electronic devices, digital signal processing, conditional access systems, network switches/routers, remote computer access, virtual machines, computer hardware, computer software, computer graphics, telecommunications (including standards), and mobile devices.
